1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 e6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 Bb4 $6 {This is the so-called,
Pin Variation. It is simply bad, BUT YOU NEED TO KNOW SOME LINES BY HEART!...
and then get a big advantage or sometimes even a winning game!} 6. e5 Nd5 (6...
Qa5 $2 {Attacking e5 and c3 but losing by force. 6...Qc7? leads to the same
thing.} 7. exf6 Bxc3+ 8. bxc3 Qxc3+ 9. Qd2 Qxa1 10. c3 {Threatening to win the
queen by Nb3 followed by Bd3.} Qb1 (10... gxf6 $2 11. Nb3 Qb1 12. Bd3 $18) 11.
Bd3 Qb6 12. fxg7 Rg8 13. Qh6 Qc7 14. O-O (14. Kd2 $5 $18 {also wins.}) 14...
Qe5 15. Bxh7 Qxg7 16. Bxg8 Qxg8 17. Qf6 $18) (6... Ne4 $6 7. Qd3 $1 $14 {
This is only slightly better for White, but without any memorization!!} (7. Qg4
$1 $16 {/+- This is very strong but with loooots of analysis to remember ! I
dont know if it is worth it in this very rare position when we have an easier
alternative!}) 7... f5 (7... Nxc3 8. bxc3 Bc5 9. Qg3 $1 $16 {Often the key
move in these positions. The queen protects e5 and c3 while also attacking g7.}
) 8. exf6 Nxf6 9. a3 Be7 10. Be3 $14) 7. Bd2 $1 Nxc3 (7... Bxc3 $2 8. bxc3 d6 (
8... Qc7 9. f4 $16 Nxc3 $2 10. Qf3 Nd5 11. Nb5 $18) 9. Qg4 $1 Kf8 10. exd6 Qxd6
11. Qf3 $16 Nc6 12. Nxc6 Qxc6 13. c4 $3 (13. Bd3 $16 {Kotronias}) 13... Ne7 14.
Qa3 $18) 8. bxc3 Be7 (8... Ba5 $2 9. Qg4 O-O 10. Bd3 d6 11. Nf3 $3 $18 g6 (
11... dxe5 12. Bxh7+ Kxh7 13. Qh5+ Kg8 14. Ng5 $18) 12. h4 dxe5 13. h5 f5 14.
Qg3 $18) (8... Bf8 9. Bd3 $16) 9. Qg4 O-O (9... g6 10. Nb5 $16) (9... Kf8 10.
Nb5 $3 Nc6 11. Qg3 $16 {SUPER SOS !!! THE KEY SQUARE FOR OUR QUEEN IN THESE
LINES IS g3 !!! From there, it protects both e5 and c3..and it is targeting
g7plus the dark squares in general!}) 10. Bh6 g6 11. h4 $3 {Better than 11.
Bxf8 when Black gets some compensation for the exchange.} Qa5 (11... Qc7 12.
Qg3 $1 Nc6 13. Nxc6 Qxc6 14. h5 $18) 12. Qg3 $16 d6 $1 (12... Rd8 13. h5 $18 {
Kotronias}) 13. Nb5 $3 Nc6 (13... dxe5 14. Qxe5 f6 15. Qc7 $3 $18) 14. Bxf8
Kxf8 15. Nxd6 $3 (15. exd6 $6 Bf6) 15... Qxe5+ 16. Qxe5 Nxe5 17. Rd1 b6 18. Rh3
$16 {(analysis by Kotronias and by me)} *

