{The following model games are dedicated to the line} 1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. exd5
cxd5 4. Bd3 Nc6 5. c3 Nf6 6. Bf4 Bg4 7. Qb3 Qd7 {This has always been the main
line. The major diffrence between Qc8 and Qd7, is that Black might plan Bd6 in
the future. By studying the model games, you will get better understanding of
the typical positional ideas in these positions.} *

