{The following model games are dedicated to the line} 1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. exd5
cxd5 4. Bd3 Nf6 5. c3 e6 $2 {This very common is a huge mistake. Black can't
afford to block his light squared Bishop in the pawn chain. In fact, our aim
in this whole line is to force Black to play ...e6 By studying the model games,
you will get better understanding of such positions.} *

