1. e4 d6 {Pirc and Modern Defence --> PART 2} (1... Nf6 {Alekhine Defence -->
PART 3}) (1... d5 {Scandinavian Defence --> PART 4}) (1... Nc6 {Nimzovich
Defence and other minor options --> PART 1}) *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "2024.01.08"]
[Round "?"]
[White "PART 1: 1.e4 MINOR OPTIONS"]
[Black "THEORETICAL OVERVIEW"]
